Anak kost yang suka dipuji, even hal terkecil sekalipun. Pernah jadi Koordinator PMB Fasilkom UI Angkatan 2023, udah merasakan banyak pengalaman dan rasa campur aduk di Angkatan 2023. Event terfavorit Sabtu Ceria 2, terutama Sesi Evaluasi ;)
message: Halo Teman-teman CS UI 2023! Selamat telah menjadi bagian dari Fasilkom UI 2023 dan Cerita 23 yang begitu panjang dan menyenangkan tentunya. Gua juga ingin mengucapkan Terima Kasih kepada kalian yang telah berpartisipasi dan aktif dalam kegiatan PMB Fasilkom 2023. Tanpa kalian, pekerjaan Gua sebagai Koordinator Angkatan tentunya tidak akan mudah. Pesan dari Gua untuk kalian singkat aja, jangan lupa untuk selalu menjaga solidaritas antar angkatan, menjaga budaya Fasilkom, dan hormat satu sama lain. Akhir kata, Gua mau ucapin Terima Kasih kepada kalian karena telah memberikan Gua pengalaman yang tak terlupakan selama Gua menjadi Koordinator Angkatan. Pengalaman ini akan selalu Gua ingat untuk seumur hidup Gua. Berakhirnya masa Koordinator Gua bukan berarti akhir dari CS UI 2023, melainkan awal baru bagi kita. Semoga kedepannya CS UI 2023 makin solid! Semangat buat kita semua!

Hi my name's Farrel and I'm a Bogor native but with Aceh-Jawa blood but don't expect me speaking in any tribal language fluently because I have 0 knowledge on them (I'm deeply sorry to my ancestors). I don't really know what to put here so I'll just list my hobbies or favorite medias. Don't let my apperance fool you since I'm a weeb, I like animes and mangas. My favorite genres tend to be seinen, slice of life, mystery, or even romance. My favorites so far are Evangelion, Berserk, Steins;Gate, Monogatari Series, JoJo, and Slam Dunk. I'm a BIG fan of music to a point where it's way easier to find genres that I dislike rather than my favorites. Top artists/bands in my list are Tatsuro Yamashita, Lamp, Radiohead, Daft Punk, King Gizzard & The Lizard Wizard, Polyphia, and many more. To add to that I also am a guitarist who's in their Math-Rock phase however currently I'm still trying to find a good deal on an electric guitar since I desperately want one. I also am into games, currently have Elden Ring, Cyberpunk 2077, Forza Horizon 5 in my library but I can't play them because I have no rig to play it on (can't wait to emulate the switch too so that I can play zelda). My favorite games tend to just be ridiculously difficult games like Hades or the Dark Souls series but I'm also open to more competitive games like counter-strike, valorant, and other stupid games we play with our friends. And finally, my one other hobby is walking around in parks since I find public parks really calming especially with their quietness. They're probably my go to place if i want to study, work, or even on a date
